east.desc: A dirt path leads away through the great field north of Midgaard.

name: The Great Chessboard Of Midgaard
desc: You stand in the archway of the Chessboard of Midgaard.  The giant wooden gate is rusted open.    A narrow dirt path leads eastwards into the thick grass and the chessboard opens up to the west.
